## üöÄ Quick Start
```bash
# Clone and install Penguin
git clone https://github.com/maximooch/penguin.git
cd penguin

# Install Penguin (recommended with UV)
pip install -e .

# Set your API key
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your API key

# Run Penguin
penguin  # CLI interface
# OR
penguin-web  # Web interface 
```

